author: The Current
description:
In 2014, singer-songwriter Jake Bugg visited the Forum at Minnesota Public Radio, just a month shy of his 20th birthday.

Check out the full performance of “Me and You” on our Youtube channel.
title: Jake Bugg performs "Me and You" in 2014 #JakeBugg

author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of José González featuring previously unreleased footage, from when he visited The Current studio back in 2015.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 With the Ink of a Ghost
00:05:00 Every Age
00:08:21 Leaf Off/The Cave

Musicians
José González — vocals, guitar

Producer – Derrick Stevens
